Package: AutoStat
Title: Automated Statistical Analysis Using Large Language Models
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Xianyang", "Zhang",
    email = "zhangxiany@stat.tamu.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Leverages large language models (GPT-5, Claude Sonnet 4.5, Gemini 2.5) to
    automate statistical analysis tasks. Users provide a dataset and research question,
    and the package determines appropriate analysis methods, executes them, and produces
    interpretable reports with professional visualizations.
